about.summary: ISO language, territory, currency, script and character codes. Provides ISO 639 language codes, ISO 3166 territory codes, ISO 4217 currency codes, ISO 15924 script codes, and the ISO 8859 character codes as well as the UN M.49 area codes.

name: r-isocodes
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2020.03.16" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-isocodes
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/ISOcodes_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/ISOcodes/ISOcodes_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 160eb4ea23be53305e4e728002c8f5d3852d89155f538deccb734e7c8ad4e1c3

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('ISOcodes')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('ISOcodes')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=ISOcodes
  license: GPL-2
  summary: ISO language, territory, currency, script and character codes. Provides ISO 639 language codes, ISO 3166 territory codes, ISO 4217 currency codes, ISO
    15924 script codes, and the ISO 8859 character codes as well as the UN M.49 area codes.
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - stevierene82
    - conda-forge/r
